name: Cyrce's Circlet
description: Sea dogs and tale spinners tell stories of a mythical siren that could lure even the stubbornest sailors to a watery grave.

spells.description:
Use: Channel to vent flames for 2 sec, dealing 2.4 million Fire damage split between all nearby enemies.

Mechanical enemies become Superheated, taking 114,596  additional Fire damage when struck by your next harmful ability. (2 Min Cooldown)

Use: Hold out the feather for 1 sec to strike with the power of the storm, crashing down on the target location and inflicting 928,494 Nature damage split between nearby enemies. (1 Min 30 Sec Cooldown)

Equip: Gain Ascendance every 8 seconds spent in combat.

Ascendance grants 89 of a random secondary stat for 15 sec, stacking up to 10 times.

This is a Nerubian embellishment.
